    <link>https://vkvk17.github.io/posts/2026-03-28-opensuse-tumbleweed-%E5%92%8C-kde-%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B/</link>
